These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, iced-tea, almond-milk
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, rat, fish, cat
1. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
5. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk | mirinda | almond-milk | iced-tea |
| Pet        | goldfish | rat   | cat | fish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, horror, spy, time-travel
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, pakistani, australian, mexican
1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the spanish is on the left of the australian##1
3. the australian is in an odd position##4
4. the spanish is the person watching family movies##1
5. the pakistani is on the right of the australian##1
6. the spanish is the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | family  | horror  | time-travel |
| Nationality   | mexican    | spanish | australian | pakistani    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, cabbage, corn, mango
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, adventure, action, crime
1. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
2. the person eating corn is in an even position##4
3. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
4. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
5. the person watching drama movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating corn##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | mango | corn | cabbage    | broccoli      |
| Movie-Genre   | action        | crime     | drama | adventure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, card-games, camping, singing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, pop, rock, jazz
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the fan of soul and the fan of jazz##2
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the fan of rock is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
5. the fan of pop is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | singing | fishing | card-games | camping |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | soul   | pop    | jazz  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, dubstep, rock, metal
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, nigerian, brazilian, canadian
1. the fan of rock is on the right of the canadian##1
2. the nigerian is the fan of metal##1
3. the brazilian is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
4. the fan of dubstep is on the far left##1
5. the fan of rock is in an odd position##4
6. the pakistani is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep  | reggae    | rock   | metal       |
| Nationality   | pakistani | canadian | brazilian | nigerian |

