.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, sports, time-travel, crime
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, subway, trike, train
1. the person driving the train is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the person driving the train is the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
6. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | crime | time-travel | sports    |
| Transport     | train | trike  | boat     | subway |

