.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, chef, security-guard, designer
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, mouse, hamster, turtle
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the chef##3
2. the designer is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the designer##3
4. the designer is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the paramedic is between the designer and the chef##2
6. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the mouse is between the paramedic and the owner of the hamster##2
8. the paramedic is on the left or right of the chef##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | chef | paramedic      | designer | security-guard |
| Pet   | rabbit  | turtle | mouse    | hamster            |

