4 different pets are kept: goldfish, lizard, hedgehog, dog
1. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
2. the person eating lime is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the lizard and the person eating cherry##2
4. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating cherry is the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | pomegranate | strawberry   | lime | cherry |
| Pet    | dog     | lizard | goldfish     | hedgehog  |

