.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, milk, tea, mirinda
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, indie, trance, r&b
1. the person drinking coffee is the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of classical is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the fan of r&b is between the fan of classical and the person drinking tea##2
4. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
6. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | milk       | tea   | coffee | mirinda |
| Music-Genre   | trance | indie | r&b        | classical    |

