.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, 7up, lemonade, sprite
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, rugby, handball, tennis
1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk   | sprite   | 7up      | lemonade      |
| Sport      | rugby | handball | tennis | soccer |

