2. the fan of rock is in an even position##4
3. the person eating onion is in an even position##4
4. the person eating cauliflower is on the far right##1
5. the person eating spinach is between the fan of house and the fan of rock##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | orange | onion  | spinach  | cauliflower |
| Music-Genre   | indie  | rock | techno | house   |

