2. the person watching time-travel movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
6. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | disaster | time-travel | horror |
| Pet           | guinea-pig     | cat     | hamster   | chinchilla         |

