.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, drawing, filmmaking, gardening
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, badminton, snowboarding, swimming
1. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | gardening | drawing         | camping   | filmmaking |
| Sport   | snowboarding    | badminton | swimming | cricket   |

