.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, video-games, camping, puzzles
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, baseball, weightlifting, handball
1. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | collecting | camping    | puzzles |
| Sport   | snowboarding   | weightlifting  | handball | baseball     |

