.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, card-games, baking, photography
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, thai, argentine, italian
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
3. the thai is the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the argentine is on the left or right of the thai##3
5. the thai is between the italian and the argentine##2
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | photography   | baking | woodworking | card-games    |
| Nationality   | argentine | thai  | italian     | egyptian |

