.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, mirinda, sprite, cola
There 4 different types of food: garlic, lemon, broccoli, mango
1. the person eating lemon is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
3. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating mango##1
5. the person eating mango is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the person eating broccoli is in an even position##4
7. the person eating garlic is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | cola | soy-milk    | sprite       | mirinda |
| Food       | lemon  | broccoli | mango | garlic  |

