.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, russian, french, indian
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, snowmobile, subway, helicopter
1. the brazilian is on the left of the indian##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
3. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the french##1
5. the brazilian is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
6. the person driving the van is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | russian | french | brazilian  | indian |
| Transport     | van      | subway       | snowmobile | helicopter     |

