.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, videographer, accountant, scientist
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, train, ship, skateboard
1. the videographer is in an even position##4
2. the videographer is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
3. the person driving the train is between the police-officer and the person driving the scooter##2
4. the videographer is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the scientist##1
6. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | police-officer | accountant   | scientist | videographer |
| Transport   | skateboard          | train | scooter         | ship  |

 